title: Week 1 recap
itunes:title: Week 1 recap
description:
A room full of heroes -- Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler, Gregg Rosenthal and Chris Wesseling -- reinstate their late-night rants and reviews to bring you the first recap of the 2014 regular season. The guys also welcome in Kevin Patra and talk about some of the biggest takeaways you need to know from Week 1.
